"{\"uid\": \"myrepublica.nagariknetwork.com-news-olympic-dreams\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Subscribe Now The Rio Olympics is in full swing and, as usual, our athletes who have been selected will come back home without any medals.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 139, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 19, \"end\": 31, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0314614524287676e-17, \"text\": \"Rio Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"full swing\", \"from\": 37, \"to\": 47}, {\"ngram\": \"our athletes\", \"from\": 63, \"to\": 75}, {\"ngram\": \"any medals\", \"from\": 127, \"to\": 137}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We really do not expect much from our athletes in such international events because we know that we lack the resources, infrastructure and everything else needed to compete in the international level.\", \"from\": 140, \"to\": 340, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our athletes\", \"from\": 174, \"to\": 186}, {\"ngram\": \"such international events\", \"from\": 190, \"to\": 215}, {\"ngram\": \"the resources\", \"from\": 245, \"to\": 258}, {\"ngram\": \"infrastructure\", \"from\": 260, \"to\": 274}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 279, \"to\": 289}, {\"ngram\": \"the international level\", \"from\": 316, \"to\": 339}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So to expect our athletes to win an Olympic Gold is like expecting KP Oli to send a Nepali to Mars on a rickshaw.\", \"from\": 341, \"to\": 454, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 408, \"end\": 414, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KP_Sharma_Oli\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"KP Oli\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KP_Sharma_Oli\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KP_Sharma_Oli\"}, {\"begin\": 425, \"end\": 431, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\", \"score\": 0.9999999899414433, \"rank\": 8.732229380646535e-09, \"text\": \"Nepali\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our athletes\", \"from\": 354, \"to\": 366}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic Gold\", \"from\": 374, \"to\": 389}, {\"ngram\": \"Mars\", \"from\": 435, \"to\": 439}, {\"ngram\": \"a rickshaw\", \"from\": 443, \"to\": 453}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is not going to happen anytime soon but it's good to dream and sometimes dreams do come true but only if we work hard to fulfill them.Our government does not care about sports.\", \"from\": 455, \"to\": 634, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"dreams\", \"from\": 531, \"to\": 537}, {\"ngram\": \"Our government\", \"from\": 592, \"to\": 606}, {\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 627, \"to\": 633}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Well, our government actually does not care about anything other than how to steal from the national coffer.\", \"from\": 635, \"to\": 743, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our government\", \"from\": 641, \"to\": 655}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 685, \"to\": 693}, {\"ngram\": \"the national coffer\", \"from\": 723, \"to\": 742}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We have the National Sports Council (NSC), also known as No Sports Council, because the person heading the organization is a political appointee and he or she will only think about how to siphon off the organization's budget instead of helping to develop sports and provide opportunities and resources to our athletes.We have hundreds of sports organizations in the country and most of them are headed by people who were never active in sports.\", \"from\": 744, \"to\": 1188, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 756, \"end\": 779, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Sports_Council\", \"score\": 0.9659866423458788, \"rank\": 0.03521096114985126, \"text\": \"National Sports Council\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Sports_Council\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Sports_Council\"}, {\"begin\": 781, \"end\": 784, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_National_Security_Council\", \"score\": 0.9999987576955832, \"rank\": 1.2358003324702653e-06, \"text\": \"NSC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_National_Security_Council\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_National_Security_Council\"}, {\"begin\": 804, \"end\": 818, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sport_England\", \"score\": 0.9984051120615314, \"rank\": 0.001597435669344798, \"text\": \"Sports Council\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sport_England\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sport_England\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the person\", \"from\": 828, \"to\": 838}, {\"ngram\": \"the organization\", \"from\": 847, \"to\": 863}, {\"ngram\": \"a political appointee\", \"from\": 867, \"to\": 888}, {\"ngram\": \"the organization's budget\", \"from\": 943, \"to\": 968}, {\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 999, \"to\": 1005}, {\"ngram\": \"opportunities\", \"from\": 1018, \"to\": 1031}, {\"ngram\": \"resources\", \"from\": 1036, \"to\": 1045}, {\"ngram\": \"our athletes\", \"from\": 1049, \"to\": 1061}, {\"ngram\": \"hundreds\", \"from\": 1070, \"to\": 1078}, {\"ngram\": \"sports organizations\", \"from\": 1082, \"to\": 1102}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 1106, \"to\": 1117}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1149, \"to\": 1155}, {\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 1181, \"to\": 1187}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A guy in my neighborhood is a district committee member of ANFA, the football body in our country.\", \"from\": 1189, \"to\": 1287, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1248, \"end\": 1252, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/All_Nepal_Football_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5655172774407906e-29, \"text\": \"ANFA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/All_Nepal_Football_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/All_Nepal_Football_Association\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A guy\", \"from\": 1189, \"to\": 1194}, {\"ngram\": \"my neighborhood\", \"from\": 1198, \"to\": 1213}, {\"ngram\": \"a district committee member\", \"from\": 1217, \"to\": 1244}, {\"ngram\": \"the football body\", \"from\": 1254, \"to\": 1271}, {\"ngram\": \"our country\", \"from\": 1275, \"to\": 1286}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He has never played football in his life.\", \"from\": 1288, \"to\": 1329, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"football\", \"from\": 1308, \"to\": 1316}, {\"ngram\": \"his life\", \"from\": 1320, \"to\": 1328}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He only knows how to flatter the 'high-profile' people while ignoring everyone else.\", \"from\": 1330, \"to\": 1414, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 'high-profile' people\", \"from\": 1359, \"to\": 1384}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 1400, \"to\": 1408}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He does not even know much about international football except Pele and Maradona.\", \"from\": 1415, \"to\": 1496, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1487, \"end\": 1495, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diego_Maradona\", \"score\": 0.9999366112566215, \"rank\": 6.339276177595573e-05, \"text\": \"Maradona\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diego_Maradona\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diego_Maradona\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"international football\", \"from\": 1448, \"to\": 1470}, {\"ngram\": \"Pele\", \"from\": 1478, \"to\": 1482}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pele last played in the 70s and it's been more than twenty years since Maradona hung up his boots and started putting on weight.\", \"from\": 1497, \"to\": 1625, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1568, \"end\": 1576, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diego_Maradona\", \"score\": 0.9999366112566215, \"rank\": 6.339276177595573e-05, \"text\": \"Maradona\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diego_Maradona\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diego_Maradona\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Pele\", \"from\": 1497, \"to\": 1501}, {\"ngram\": \"the 70s\", \"from\": 1517, \"to\": 1524}, {\"ngram\": \"more than twenty years\", \"from\": 1539, \"to\": 1561}, {\"ngram\": \"his boots\", \"from\": 1585, \"to\": 1594}, {\"ngram\": \"weight\", \"from\": 1618, \"to\": 1624}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think he knows Messi but of course who does not.I bet that the people running the athletics association can not even jog let alone run a 5 km race.\", \"from\": 1626, \"to\": 1775, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1643, \"end\": 1648, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lionel_Messi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.096360092620093e-32, \"text\": \"Messi\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lionel_Messi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lionel_Messi\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 1656, \"to\": 1662}, {\"ngram\": \"the people\", \"from\": 1687, \"to\": 1697}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletics association\", \"from\": 1706, \"to\": 1731}, {\"ngram\": \"a 5 km race\", \"from\": 1763, \"to\": 1774}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even if you are not an athlete, at least do something good for the association you are heading.\", \"from\": 1776, \"to\": 1871, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an athlete\", \"from\": 1796, \"to\": 1806}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1820, \"to\": 1829}, {\"ngram\": \"the association\", \"from\": 1839, \"to\": 1854}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We have so many sports bodies in this country and half of them do not even conduct any sports activities at all.\", \"from\": 1872, \"to\": 1984, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"so many sports bodies\", \"from\": 1880, \"to\": 1901}, {\"ngram\": \"this country\", \"from\": 1905, \"to\": 1917}, {\"ngram\": \"half\", \"from\": 1922, \"to\": 1926}, {\"ngram\": \"any sports activities\", \"from\": 1955, \"to\": 1976}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The people in such organizations are in it not to develop their respective sports but to wait for international sports bodies to send them free air tickets and stipend so that they can attend conferences abroad.Yes, politics is everywhere and nearly all of our so-called chairpersons of such sports organizations are politically affiliated.\", \"from\": 1985, \"to\": 2325, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The people\", \"from\": 1985, \"to\": 1995}, {\"ngram\": \"such organizations\", \"from\": 1999, \"to\": 2017}, {\"ngram\": \"their respective sports\", \"from\": 2043, \"to\": 2066}, {\"ngram\": \"international sports bodies\", \"from\": 2083, \"to\": 2110}, {\"ngram\": \"free air tickets\", \"from\": 2124, \"to\": 2140}, {\"ngram\": \"conferences\", \"from\": 2177, \"to\": 2188}, {\"ngram\": \"politics\", \"from\": 2201, \"to\": 2209}, {\"ngram\": \"nearly all\", \"from\": 2228, \"to\": 2238}, {\"ngram\": \"our so-called chairpersons\", \"from\": 2242, \"to\": 2268}, {\"ngram\": \"such sports organizations\", \"from\": 2272, \"to\": 2297}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And major sports associations seem to have factions and even two different organizations fighting with each other over who is the authentic one and who is not.\", \"from\": 2326, \"to\": 2485, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"major sports associations\", \"from\": 2330, \"to\": 2355}, {\"ngram\": \"factions\", \"from\": 2369, \"to\": 2377}, {\"ngram\": \"even two different organizations\", \"from\": 2382, \"to\": 2414}, {\"ngram\": \"the authentic one\", \"from\": 2452, \"to\": 2469}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We even had two different Olympics Committees until sometime ago.\", \"from\": 2486, \"to\": 2551, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"two different Olympics Committees\", \"from\": 2498, \"to\": 2531}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The IOC, the main Olympics body recognized one while our Supreme Court said the other one was the real one.\", \"from\": 2552, \"to\": 2659, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2556, \"end\": 2559, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.2481152917717048e-23, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 2609, \"end\": 2622, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Supreme_Court_of_India\", \"score\": 0.9968427756152003, \"rank\": 0.003142167118529257, \"text\": \"Supreme Court\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Supreme_Court_of_India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Supreme_Court_of_India\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the main Olympics body\", \"from\": 2561, \"to\": 2583}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And everybody was confused about which one was the one and which one was not.\", \"from\": 2660, \"to\": 2737, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everybody\", \"from\": 2664, \"to\": 2673}, {\"ngram\": \"one\", \"from\": 2699, \"to\": 2702}, {\"ngram\": \"which one\", \"from\": 2719, \"to\": 2728}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I hope the controversy is over now and our so-called saviors can go back to help our athletes instead of only helping themselves.The last and the only time we ever won any medals was in Seoul when Bidhan Lama won us a bronze in Taekwondo even though it was just a demonstration event.\", \"from\": 2738, \"to\": 3022, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2924, \"end\": 2929, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seoul\", \"score\": 0.9997745932817408, \"rank\": 0.00022545752019942803, \"text\": \"Seoul\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seoul\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seoul\"}, {\"begin\": 2935, \"end\": 2946, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bidhan_Lama\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bidhan Lama\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bidhan_Lama\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bidhan_Lama\"}, {\"begin\": 2966, \"end\": 2975, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taekwondo\", \"score\": 0.9999999999977263, \"rank\": 2.3109880966990454e-12, \"text\": \"Taekwondo\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taekwondo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taekwondo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the controversy\", \"from\": 2745, \"to\": 2760}, {\"ngram\": \"our so-called saviors\", \"from\": 2777, \"to\": 2798}, {\"ngram\": \"our athletes\", \"from\": 2819, \"to\": 2831}, {\"ngram\": \"the only time\", \"from\": 2880, \"to\": 2893}, {\"ngram\": \"any medals\", \"from\": 2906, \"to\": 2916}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2951, \"to\": 2953}, {\"ngram\": \"a bronze\", \"from\": 2954, \"to\": 2962}, {\"ngram\": \"just a demonstration event\", \"from\": 2995, \"to\": 3021}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This time around, we had the youngest athlete ever in the Olympics and we are happy that Gaurika Singh won her heat even though she stood 31st among 34 athletes.\", \"from\": 3023, \"to\": 3184, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3112, \"end\": 3125, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaurika_Singh\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gaurika Singh\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaurika_Singh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaurika_Singh\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the youngest athlete\", \"from\": 3048, \"to\": 3068}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3077, \"to\": 3089}, {\"ngram\": \"her heat\", \"from\": 3130, \"to\": 3138}, {\"ngram\": \"31st\", \"from\": 3161, \"to\": 3165}, {\"ngram\": \"34 athletes\", \"from\": 3172, \"to\": 3183}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Our athletes in other sports also failed to advance to the next round in their respective events.\", \"from\": 3185, \"to\": 3282, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Our athletes\", \"from\": 3185, \"to\": 3197}, {\"ngram\": \"other sports\", \"from\": 3201, \"to\": 3213}, {\"ngram\": \"the next round\", \"from\": 3240, \"to\": 3254}, {\"ngram\": \"their respective events\", \"from\": 3258, \"to\": 3281}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Well, they did their best and we should be proud of them.So when will we win another Olympic medal?\", \"from\": 3283, \"to\": 3382, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"another Olympic medal\", \"from\": 3360, \"to\": 3381}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Well, with the way things are going in the country, we might even fail to win a Gold in SAG Games.\", \"from\": 3383, \"to\": 3481, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 3394, \"to\": 3401}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 3402, \"to\": 3408}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 3422, \"to\": 3433}, {\"ngram\": \"a Gold\", \"from\": 3461, \"to\": 3467}, {\"ngram\": \"SAG Games\", \"from\": 3471, \"to\": 3480}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Every time there is an international sports event, we send more officials than athletes.\", \"from\": 3482, \"to\": 3570, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an international sports event\", \"from\": 3502, \"to\": 3531}, {\"ngram\": \"more officials\", \"from\": 3541, \"to\": 3555}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 3561, \"to\": 3569}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It seems that even those athletes who are selected for such events are not allowed to participate if they are not politically affiliated or do not have folks who have connections with our officials.\", \"from\": 3571, \"to\": 3769, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"even those athletes\", \"from\": 3585, \"to\": 3604}, {\"ngram\": \"such events\", \"from\": 3626, \"to\": 3637}, {\"ngram\": \"folks\", \"from\": 3723, \"to\": 3728}, {\"ngram\": \"connections\", \"from\": 3738, \"to\": 3749}, {\"ngram\": \"our officials\", \"from\": 3755, \"to\": 3768}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A few years ago, we heard about how one of our athletes had to participate in a sports event abroad after her coach bought her the tickets and she came back home with a Gold.Our so-called sports officials have no shame.\", \"from\": 3770, \"to\": 3989, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our athletes\", \"from\": 3813, \"to\": 3825}, {\"ngram\": \"a sports event\", \"from\": 3848, \"to\": 3862}, {\"ngram\": \"her coach\", \"from\": 3876, \"to\": 3885}, {\"ngram\": \"the tickets\", \"from\": 3897, \"to\": 3908}, {\"ngram\": \"a Gold\", \"from\": 3937, \"to\": 3943}, {\"ngram\": \"Our so-called sports officials\", \"from\": 3944, \"to\": 3974}, {\"ngram\": \"no shame\", \"from\": 3980, \"to\": 3988}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They are happy with the way things are going because if that changes then our athletes will get the resources to do better, but it will be the end of free lunch for our officials.\", \"from\": 3990, \"to\": 4169, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 4010, \"to\": 4017}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 4018, \"to\": 4024}, {\"ngram\": \"our athletes\", \"from\": 4064, \"to\": 4076}, {\"ngram\": \"the resources\", \"from\": 4086, \"to\": 4099}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 4129, \"to\": 4136}, {\"ngram\": \"free lunch\", \"from\": 4140, \"to\": 4150}, {\"ngram\": \"our officials\", \"from\": 4155, \"to\": 4168}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We have a new government now and let us hope that our new Youth and Sports Minister will actually do something for the youth and sports in this country ra